nUPDATE multiplier SET value = 3000 WHERE uid = 'dce742ae-6274-4869-a9ee-cdf123268344';\nUPDATE multiplier SET value = 1000 WHERE uid = '7d04235c-8459-4980-84db-6cc0501b1777';\nUPDATE multiplier SET value = 1000 WHERE uid = '85559876-f4ca-4278-8f7f-1b195157a69d';\nUPDATE multiplier SET value = 3000 WHERE uid = '59a578bd-a330-4aba-9cc5-722ef533afa8';\nUPDATE multiplier SET value = 2000 WHERE uid = 'd1116b08-f275-4381-93d5-a8f738b041fc';\nUPDATE multiplier SET value = 5000 WHERE uid = 'c23f115e-0789-422e-b661-56fa4f86b9f7';\nUPDATE multiplier SET value = 5000 WHERE uid = 'bdf526c6-6708-433e-b68c-d746b240a6df';\nUPDATE multiplier SET value = 2000 WHERE uid = '0ba1399b-c9b5-4684-8af5-e0d44bb166b1';\nUPDATE multiplier SET value = 6000 WHERE uid = '57ca316f-2778-4c3b-a9b4-330c6984ea62';\nUPDATE multiplier SET value = 4000 WHERE uid = '0b3d90c9-863f-43e5-8bfc-446e9ca71dc3';\nUPDATE multiplier SET value = 4000 WHERE uid = '99a6eb0d-3a97-4876-8a19-fb40658873c7';\nUPDATE multiplier SET value = 3000 WHERE uid = '80e692a0-ec9c-47ea-9315-43f53bc03b7b';\nUPDATE multiplier SET value = 2000 WHERE uid = '3f0cc590-04f6-468a-9ebc-562fcc591191';\nUPDATE multiplier SET value = 5000 WHERE uid = 'd76a8db2-343e-4608-af73-e52b320e3743';\nUPDATE multiplier SET value = 2000 WHERE uid = 'd0f412f4-a64b-4a68-8cae-f24901871e81';\nUPDATE multiplier SET value = 2000 WHERE uid = '7cdc0ac9-773c-4d05-9509-ee2bfca97c6f';\nUPDATE multiplier SET value = 3000 WHERE uid = '7d0bfc14-81b5-4327-947f-1b8826ccdd4a';\nUPDATE multiplier SET value = 6000 WHERE uid = '94e23ae4-651a-4c22-a26c-d79e9a3b94a2';\n```","project":{"id":215675,"name":"[consumer_loyalty][prod] Halve multipliers on gift cards"},"entityState":{"id":215675,"name":"[consumer_loyalty][prod] Halve multipliers on gift cards"}},{"id":215651,"name":"[business_premium][prod] - Activate new merchant BULK","description":"<!--markdown-->## Why\nref: https://github.com/satispay-tech/bck_helpdesk_merchant2/issues/49\n\n## What\nExecute the following migration from the attached file:\n\n```\ncurl --request POST \\\n  --url  'https://internal-admin-api.satispay.aws/merchant/business-premium/v2/subscriptions' \\\n--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n--data '{\n    \"merchant_id\": \"{{merchant_id}}\",\n    \"start_date\": \"{{now}}\",\n    \"plan_id\": \"{{plan_id}}\",\n    \"operator\": \"admin\"\n}'\n```","project":{"id":215651,"name":"[business_premium][prod] - Activate new merchant BULK"},"entityState":{"id":215651,"name":"[business_premium][prod] - Activate new merchant BULK"}},{"id":215642,"name":"[fee][prod] - Set custom fee for merchant","description":"<!--markdown-->## WHY\nRef: https://github.com/satispay-tech/bck_helpdesk_merchant2/issues/54\n\n## WHAT\nPerform the following curl:\n\n```\ncurl --request POST \\\n  --url 'https://internal-admin-api.satispay.aws/merchant/fee-and-invoice/v1.1/issuers/MERCHANT/31534311-b344-43af-9ff0-1084bf88e2a3/fee_configurations' \\\n  --header 'content-type: application/json' \\\n  --data '{\n    \"configurations\": [\n        {\n            \"type\": \"PERCENTAGE\",\n            \"amount\": 48,\n            \"target\": \"BUSINESS\",\n            \"filters\": [\n                {\n                    \"action\": \"SHOP_MODEL\",\n                    \"payload\": {\n                        \"operator\": \"IN\",\n                        \"target\": [\n                            \"BRICK_AND_MORTAR\",\n                            \"ON_THE_MOVE\"\n                        ]\n                    }\n                },\n                {\n                    \"action\": \"DATE\",\n                    \"payload\": {\n                        \"operator\": \"GT\",\n                        \"target\": \"{{now}}\"\n                    }\n                }\n            ]\n        },\n        {\n            \"type\": \"FIXED\",\n            \"amount\": 20,\n            \"target\": \"BUSINESS\",\n            \"filters\": [\n                {\n                    \"action\": \"SHOP_MODEL\",\n                    \"payload\": {\n                        \"operator\": \"IN\",\n                        \"target\": [\n                            \"ECOMMERCE_MOBILE\",\n                            \"ECOMMERCE_WEBSITE\",\n                            \"SOCIAL_MEDIA\"\n                        ]\n                    }\n                },\n                {\n                    \"action\": \"DATE\",\n                    \"payload\": {\n                        \"operator\": \"GT\",\n                        \"target\": \"{{now}}\"\n                    }\n                },\n                {\n                    \"action\": \"AMOUNT\",\n                    \"payload\": {\n                        \"operator\": \"GT\",\n                        \"target\": 999\n                    }\n                }\n            ]\n        },\n        {\n            \"type\": \"FIXED\",\n            \"amount\": 0,\n            \"target\": \"BUSINESS\",\n            \"filters\": [\n                {\n                    \"action\": \"SHOP_MODEL\",\n                    \"payload\": {\n                        \"operator\": \"IN\",\n                        \"target\": [\n                            \"ECOMMERCE_MOBILE\",\n                            \"ECOMMERCE_WEBSITE\",\n                            \"SOCIAL_MEDIA\"\n                        ]\n                    }\n                },\n                {\n                    \"action\": \"DATE\",\n                    \"payload\": {\n                        \"operator\": \"GT\",\n                        \"target\": \"{{now}}\"\n                    }\n                },\n                {\n                    \"action\": \"AMOUNT\",\n                    \"payload\": {\n                        \"operator\": \"LE\",\n                        \"target\": 999\n                    }\n                }\n            ]\n        },\n        {\n            \"type\": \"PERCENTAGE\",\n            \"amount\": 50,\n            \"target\": \"BUSINESS\",\n            \"filters\": [\n                {\n                    \"action\": \"SHOP_MODEL\",\n                    \"payload\": {\n                        \"operator\": \"IN\",\n                        \"target\": [\n                            \"ECOMMERCE_MOBILE\",\n                            \"ECOMMERCE_WEBSITE\",\n                            \"SOCIAL_MEDIA\"\n                        ]\n                    }\n                },\n                {\n                    \"action\": \"DATE\",\n                    \"payload\": {\n                        \"operator\": \"GT\",\n                        \"target\": \"{{now}}\"\n                    }\n                }\n            ]\n        },\n        {\n            \"type\": \"PERCENTAGE\",\n            \"amount\": 100,\n            \"target\": \"BUSINESS\",\n            \"filters\": [\n                {\n                    \"action\": \"SHOP_MODEL\",\n                    \"payload\": {\n                        \"operator\": \"IN\",\n                        \"target\": [\n                            \"SMART_VENDING_MACHINE\",\n                            \"VENDING_MACHINE\"\n                        ]\n                    }\n                },\n                {\n                    \"action\": \"DATE\",\n                    \"payload\": {\n                        \"operator\": \"GT\",\n                        \"target\": \"{{now}}\"\n                    }\n                }\n            ]\n        }\n    ]\n}'\n\n```","project":{"id":215642,"name":"[fee][prod] - Set custom fee for merchant"},"entityState":{"id":215642,"name":"[fee][prod] - Set custom fee for merchant"}},{"id":215623,"name":"[redshift][prod] SCT Incoming Backfill","description":"<!--markdown-->### WHY\nThe missing mapping of the SCT Incoming Uid caused the impossibility to correlate records\n\n### WHAT\n\nIn redshift in staging, try to backfill `sct_incoming_uid` coming from clearing_house_uid of the `e_welfare_fringe_payment_credit_fact`\n\nIn the file I have downloaded all the SCT Incoming with their `clearing_house_uid`\n\n","project":{"id":215623,"name":"[redshift][prod] SCT Incoming Backfill"},"entityState":{"id":215623,"name":"[redshift][prod] SCT Incoming Backfill"}}]}
