2026-03-06 22:57:10.238 [boundedElastic-1] DEBUG c.i.m.t.c.HttpLoggingInterceptor - <<< Response Body: {"next":"https://satispay.tpondemand.com/api/v2/UserStory?where=(Name.Contains(%22satispay_plus%22))&select=%7Bid,name,description,project:%7Bid,name%7D,entityState:%7Bid,name%7D%7D&take=5&skip=5&orderBy=CreateDate%20desc","items":[{"id":215677,"name":"[satispay_plus][prod] Increase loyalty benefit to 100%","description":"<!--markdown-->__WHY__\n\nCost reduction effect\n\n__WHAT__\n\nRun the following curls:\n```\ncurl --request PATCH \\\n  --url https://internal-admin-api.satispay.aws/consumer/satispay-plus/v1/benefits/019ad901-9be7-7450-9828-80e9ec3c3fb3 \\\n  --header 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  --header 'User-Agent: insomnia/12.3.1' \\\n  --data '{\n\t\"value\": 100,\n\t\"version\": 0\n}'\n```\n```\ncurl --request PATCH \\\n  --url https://internal-admin-api.satispay.aws/consumer/satispay-plus/v1/benefits/019ad903-d72e-7c01-ad92-098ec16d0738 \\\n  --header 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  --header 'User-Agent: insomnia/12.3.1' \\\n  --data '{\n\t\"value\": 100,\n\t\"version\": 0\n}'\n```","project":{"id":215677,"name":"[satispay_plus][prod] Increase loyalty benefit to 100%"},"entityState":{"id":215677,"name":"[satispay_plus][prod] Increase loyalty benefit to 100%"}},{"id":215101,"name":"[satispay_plus][prod] Enforce consumer_id and subscription_id check","description":"<!--markdown--># WHY\n\nTo enforce security checks for consumer_id and subscription_id pair.\n\n# WHAT\n\nExecute the following cURL:\n\n```curl\n curl --request POST \\    \n    --url https://internal-admin-api.satispay.aws/consumer/satispay-plus/v1/configurations/ \\\n    --header 'Content-Type: application/json' \\                                                                                                                                                                \n    --header 'User-Agent: insomnia/11.2.0' \\\n    --data '{\"key\":\"SUBSCRIPTION_CONSUMER_ID_VALIDATION_ENABLED\",\"value\":\"true\"}'  \n```","project":{"id":215101,"name":"[satispay_plus][prod] Enforce consumer_id and subscription_id check"},"entityState":{"id":215101,"name":"[satispay_plus][prod] Enforce consumer_id and subscription_id check"}},{"id":213169,"name":"[satispay_plus][prod] - Prefill Insurance data for subscribed users","description":"<!--markdown--># WHY\n\nWe have users already enrolled in S+ from whitelist bucket, we need to backfill manually the data for them.\n\n# WHAT\n\n```sql\n-- Step 1: Insert card numbers for each consumer (if not already exists)\nINSERT INTO insurance_allianz_card_number (uid, card_number, consumer_id, version)\nVALUES\n    (gen_random_uuid(), 'A3B7K9P2', 'efe824a0-eb8a-11e5-95cc-06cb0bb44caf'::uuid, 0),\n    (gen_random_uuid(), 'C4D8M5Q6', '89158432-e85d-4379-b5e3-952130b5357b'::uuid, 0),\n    (gen_random_uuid(), 'E9F2N7R3', '1c418178-994f-4712-99b5-1c0915bb510b'::uuid, 0),\n    (gen_random_uuid(), 'G5H8T4U9', 'b033a546-f826-45e6-8fb0-402ab10a432f'::uuid, 0),\n    (gen_random_uuid(), 'J2K6V8W3', '54745944-197c-4530-bc1b-6660523f4e6d'::uuid, 0),\n    (gen_random_uuid(), 'L7M3X9Y4', '41949f20-87b6-4a6c-b18a-1cfeda1b5429'::uuid, 0),\n    (gen_random_uuid(), 'N4P8Z2A6', '4db888a7-90da-4434-b4f2-f2f3267bdf67'::uuid, 0),\n    (gen_random_uuid(), 'Q9R5B3C7', '5f39bd45-1f53-4b19-9c28-08d3a3d75239'::uuid, 0),\n    (gen_random_uuid(), 'S2T6D8E4', '73450d1d-ade6-453c-a452-a637223abb1e'::uuid, 0),\n    (gen_random_uuid(), 'U7V3F9G2', 'd375baac-8e36-4c36-8c62-c5dd5cb985fe'::uuid, 0),\n    (gen_random_uuid(), 'W4X8H5J6', 'f415472a-47a9-4b7f-918d-c3388b8979de'::uuid, 0)\nON CONFLICT (consumer_id) DO NOTHING;\n\n-- Step 2: Insert insurance memberships for each subscription\n-- Samuele Pinta\nINSERT INTO insurance_allianz_membership (\n    uid, subscription_id, consumer_id, card_number, tracking_code, plan_level, policies,\n    status, activation_date, coverage_start_date, coverage_end_date, name, surname,\n    cancellation_date, version\n)\nVALUES (\n    gen_random_uuid(),\n    '019c5792-b3fe-7abd-902d-3d519604778e'::uuid,\n    'efe824a0-eb8a-11e5-95cc-06cb0bb44caf'::uuid,\n    'A3B7K9P2',\n    'AWP2025BASE',\n    10,\n    '[{\"number\":\"IY410005779\",\"premium\":0.32},{\"number\":\"IY410005776\",\"premium\":0.13},{\"number\":\"IY410005780\",\"premium\":0.13}]'::jsonb,\n    'ACTIVE',\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE + INTERVAL '365 days',  -- today + 365 days\n    'Samuele',\n    'Pinta',\n    NULL,\n    0\n);\n\n-- Federico Finzi\nINSERT INTO insurance_allianz_membership (\n    uid, subscription_id, consumer_id, card_number, tracking_code, plan_level, policies,\n    status, activation_date, coverage_start_date, coverage_end_date, name, surname,\n    cancellation_date, version\n)\nVALUES (\n    gen_random_uuid(),\n    '019ae132-8880-7cfc-a30e-040dbc66a7cc'::uuid,\n    '89158432-e85d-4379-b5e3-952130b5357b'::uuid,\n    'C4D8M5Q6',\n    'AWP2025BASE',\n    10,\n    '[{\"number\":\"IY410005779\",\"premium\":0.32},{\"number\":\"IY410005776\",\"premium\":0.13},{\"number\":\"IY410005780\",\"premium\":0.13}]'::jsonb,\n    'ACTIVE',\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE + INTERVAL '365 days',  -- today + 365 days\n    'Federico',\n    'Finzi',\n    NULL,\n    0\n);\n\n-- Claudia Pusceddu\nINSERT INTO insurance_allianz_membership (\n    uid, subscription_id, consumer_id, card_number, tracking_code, plan_level, policies,\n    status, activation_date, coverage_start_date, coverage_end_date, name, surname,\n    cancellation_date, version\n)\nVALUES (\n    gen_random_uuid(),\n    '019adf72-bf2e-7ac4-aaf2-613ced0d419d'::uuid,\n    '1c418178-994f-4712-99b5-1c0915bb510b'::uuid,\n    'E9F2N7R3',\n    'AWP2025BASE',\n    10,\n    '[{\"number\":\"IY410005779\",\"premium\":0.32},{\"number\":\"IY410005776\",\"premium\":0.13},{\"number\":\"IY410005780\",\"premium\":0.13}]'::jsonb,\n    'ACTIVE',\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE + INTERVAL '365 days',  -- today + 365 days\n    'Claudia',\n    'Pusceddu',\n    NULL,\n    0\n);\n\n-- Marco Ronco\nINSERT INTO insurance_allianz_membership (\n    uid, subscription_id, consumer_id, card_number, tracking_code, plan_level, policies,\n    status, activation_date, coverage_start_date, coverage_end_date, name, surname,\n    cancellation_date, version\n)\nVALUES (\n    gen_random_uuid(),\n    '019c6b67-3938-7771-a1a3-cd5820a2ea41'::uuid,\n    'b033a546-f826-45e6-8fb0-402ab10a432f'::uuid,\n    'G5H8T4U9',\n    'AWP2025BASE',\n    10,\n    '[{\"number\":\"IY410005779\",\"premium\":0.32},{\"number\":\"IY410005776\",\"premium\":0.13},{\"number\":\"IY410005780\",\"premium\":0.13}]'::jsonb,\n    'ACTIVE',\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE + INTERVAL '365 days',  -- today + 365 days\n    'Marco',\n    'Ronco',\n    NULL,\n    0\n);\n\n-- Matteo Maurizi\nINSERT INTO insurance_allianz_membership (\n    uid, subscription_id, consumer_id, card_number, tracking_code, plan_level, policies,\n    status, activation_date, coverage_start_date, coverage_end_date, name, surname,\n    cancellation_date, version\n)\nVALUES (\n    gen_random_uuid(),\n    '019ae54c-6163-76a1-b27b-967ca9613fe7'::uuid,\n    '54745944-197c-4530-bc1b-6660523f4e6d'::uuid,\n    'J2K6V8W3',\n    'AWP2025BASE',\n    10,\n    '[{\"number\":\"IY410005779\",\"premium\":0.32},{\"number\":\"IY410005776\",\"premium\":0.13},{\"number\":\"IY410005780\",\"premium\":0.13}]'::jsonb,\n    'ACTIVE',\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE + INTERVAL '365 days',  -- today + 365 days\n    'Matteo',\n    'Maurizi',\n    NULL,\n    0\n);\n\n-- Biagio Murciano\nINSERT INTO insurance_allianz_membership (\n    uid, subscription_id, consumer_id, card_number, tracking_code, plan_level, policies,\n    status, activation_date, coverage_start_date, coverage_end_date, name, surname,\n    cancellation_date, version\n)\nVALUES (\n    gen_random_uuid(),\n    '019aeb1d-accb-737b-881a-125329d24a9c'::uuid,\n    '41949f20-87b6-4a6c-b18a-1cfeda1b5429'::uuid,\n    'L7M3X9Y4',\n    'AWP2025BASE',\n    10,\n    '[{\"number\":\"IY410005779\",\"premium\":0.32},{\"number\":\"IY410005776\",\"premium\":0.13},{\"number\":\"IY410005780\",\"premium\":0.13}]'::jsonb,\n    'ACTIVE',\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE + INTERVAL '365 days',  -- today + 365 days\n    'Biagio',\n    'Murciano',\n    NULL,\n    0\n);\n\n-- Paolo Gianrossi\nINSERT INTO insurance_allianz_membership (\n    uid, subscription_id, consumer_id, card_number, tracking_code, plan_level, policies,\n    status, activation_date, coverage_start_date, coverage_end_date, name, surname,\n    cancellation_date, version\n)\nVALUES (\n    gen_random_uuid(),\n    '019adfe4-3403-727d-ab1b-0557081f6202'::uuid,\n    '4db888a7-90da-4434-b4f2-f2f3267bdf67'::uuid,\n    'N4P8Z2A6',\n    'AWP2025BASE',\n    10,\n    '[{\"number\":\"IY410005779\",\"premium\":0.32},{\"number\":\"IY410005776\",\"premium\":0.13},{\"number\":\"IY410005780\",\"premium\":0.13}]'::jsonb,\n    'ACTIVE',\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE + INTERVAL '365 days',  -- today + 365 days\n    'Paolo',\n    'Gianrossi',\n    NULL,\n    0\n);\n\n-- Federico Renis\nINSERT INTO insurance_allianz_membership (\n    uid, subscription_id, consumer_id, card_number, tracking_code, plan_level, policies,\n    status, activation_date, coverage_start_date, coverage_end_date, name, surname,\n    cancellation_date, version\n)\nVALUES (\n    gen_random_uuid(),\n    '019ae461-304f-7043-ae2a-c3a23d5b8a69'::uuid,\n    '5f39bd45-1f53-4b19-9c28-08d3a3d75239'::uuid,\n    'Q9R5B3C7',\n    'AWP2025BASE',\n    10,\n    '[{\"number\":\"IY410005779\",\"premium\":0.32},{\"number\":\"IY410005776\",\"premium\":0.13},{\"number\":\"IY410005780\",\"premium\":0.13}]'::jsonb,\n    'ACTIVE',\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE + INTERVAL '365 days',  -- today + 365 days\n    'Federico',\n    'Renis',\n    NULL,\n    0\n);\n\n-- Lorenzo Pagliero\nINSERT INTO insurance_allianz_membership (\n    uid, subscription_id, consumer_id, card_number, tracking_code, plan_level, policies,\n    status, activation_date, coverage_start_date, coverage_end_date, name, surname,\n    cancellation_date, version\n)\nVALUES (\n    gen_random_uuid(),\n    '019ae96b-5224-79cd-8b4b-ccb3c2bb07c8'::uuid,\n    '73450d1d-ade6-453c-a452-a637223abb1e'::uuid,\n    'S2T6D8E4',\n    'AWP2025BASE',\n    10,\n    '[{\"number\":\"IY410005779\",\"premium\":0.32},{\"number\":\"IY410005776\",\"premium\":0.13},{\"number\":\"IY410005780\",\"premium\":0.13}]'::jsonb,\n    'ACTIVE',\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE + INTERVAL '365 days',  -- today + 365 days\n    'Lorenzo',\n    'Pagliero',\n    NULL,\n    0\n);\n\n-- Aldo Lushkja\nINSERT INTO insurance_allianz_membership (\n    uid, subscription_id, consumer_id, card_number, tracking_code, plan_level, policies,\n    status, activation_date, coverage_start_date, coverage_end_date, name, surname,\n    cancellation_date, version\n)\nVALUES (\n    gen_random_uuid(),\n    '019b17b5-0a10-7921-b719-fc6c57881c9a'::uuid,\n    'd375baac-8e36-4c36-8c62-c5dd5cb985fe'::uuid,\n    'U7V3F9G2',\n    'AWP2025BASE',\n    10,\n    '[{\"number\":\"IY410005779\",\"premium\":0.32},{\"number\":\"IY410005776\",\"premium\":0.13},{\"number\":\"IY410005780\",\"premium\":0.13}]'::jsonb,\n    'ACTIVE',\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE + INTERVAL '365 days',  -- today + 365 days\n    'Aldo',\n    'Lushkja',\n    NULL,\n    0\n);\n\n-- Davide Bolzoni\nINSERT INTO insurance_allianz_membership (\n    uid, subscription_id, consumer_id, card_number, tracking_code, plan_level, policies,\n    status, activation_date, coverage_start_date, coverage_end_date, name, surname,\n    cancellation_date, version\n)\nVALUES (\n    gen_random_uuid(),\n    '019ade77-cbec-7414-b98d-36c3b33a88b0'::uuid,\n    'f415472a-47a9-4b7f-918d-c3388b8979de'::uuid,\n    'W4X8H5J6',\n    'AWP2025BASE',\n    10,\n    '[{\"number\":\"IY410005779\",\"premium\":0.32},{\"number\":\"IY410005776\",\"premium\":0.13},{\"number\":\"IY410005780\",\"premium\":0.13}]'::jsonb,\n    'ACTIVE',\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE,\n    CURRENT_DATE + INTERVAL '365 days',  -- today + 365 days\n    'Davide',\n    'Bolzoni',\n    NULL,\n    0\n);\n```\n```","project":{"id":213169,"name":"[satispay_plus][prod] - Prefill Insurance data for subscribed users"},"entityState":{"id":213169,"name":"[satispay_plus][prod] - Prefill Insurance data for subscribed users"}},{"id":213168,"name":"[satispay_plus][prod] - Insurance Allianz - Bootstrap - Phase 1","description":"<!--markdown--># WHY\n\nTo start production testing for new benefit INSURANCE_ALLIANZ.\n\n# WHAT\n\nWe need to run this migration script.\n\n```sql\n-- ============================================================================\n-- 0. INSURANCE ALLIANZ BENEFIT - Config\n-- ============================================================================\nINSERT INTO benefit (uid, plan_id, type, value, limitations)\nVALUES (gen_random_uuid(),\n        '019ad903-d72e-7c01-ad92-098ec16d0738',\n        'INSURANCE_ALLIANZ',\n        100, -- value can be 0 or a relevant numeric value\n        jsonb_build_object(\n                'insurance_allianz_tiers', jsonb_build_array(\n                jsonb_build_object(\n                        'plan_level', 10,\n                        'tracking_code', 'AWP2025BASE',\n                        'policies', jsonb_build_array(\n                                jsonb_build_object('number', 'IY410005779', 'premium', '0.32'),\n                                jsonb_build_object('number', 'IY410005776', 'premium', '0.13'),\n                                jsonb_build_object('number', 'IY410005780', 'premium', '0.13')\n                                    )\n                )\n                                           )\n        ))\nON CONFLICT (uid) DO NOTHING;\n\n-- Plan Level 10 - Base Tier\nINSERT INTO benefit (uid, plan_id, type, value, limitations)\nVALUES (gen_random_uuid(),\n        '019ad901-9be7-7450-9828-80e9ec3c3fb3',\n        'INSURANCE_ALLIANZ',\n        100,\n        jsonb_build_object(\n                'insurance_allianz_tiers', jsonb_build_array(\n                jsonb_build_object(\n                        'plan_level', 10,\n                        'tracking_code', 'AWP2025BASE',\n                        'policies', jsonb_build_array(\n                                jsonb_build_object('number', 'IY410005779', 'premium', '0.32'),\n                                jsonb_build_object('number', 'IY410005776', 'premium', '0.13'),\n                                jsonb_build_object('number', 'IY410005780', 'premium', '0.13')\n                                    )\n                )\n                                           )\n        ))\nON CONFLICT (uid) DO NOTHING;\n\n\n-- ============================================================================\n-- 1. INSURANCE ALLIANZ PROCESSING JOBS\n-- ============================================================================\n\nINSERT INTO configuration (key, value, description, version)\nVALUES (\n    'BENEFIT_INSURANCE_ALLIANZ_ACTIVATION_TESTER_LIST',\n    '[\"efe824a0-eb8a-11e5-95cc-06cb0bb44caf\",\"89158432-e85d-4379-b5e3-952130b5357b\",\"1c418178-994f-4712-99b5-1c0915bb510b\",\"b033a546-f826-45e6-8fb0-402ab10a432f\",\"54745944-197c-4530-bc1b-6660523f4e6d\",\"41949f20-87b6-4a6c-b18a-1cfeda1b5429\",\"4db888a7-90da-4434-b4f2-f2f3267bdf67\",\"5f39bd45-1f53-4b19-9c28-08d3a3d75239\",\"73450d1d-ade6-453c-a452-a637223abb1e\",\"d375baac-8e36-4c36-8c62-c5dd5cb985fe\",\"f415472a-47a9-4b7f-918d-c3388b8979de\",\"f8490c3d-e617-4d83-a678-1ceb5d9917b4\",\"0c5cb117-1315-4e3a-8c2e-e4db1d89b0b8\",\"698d27ae-6a19-43bc-9951-d1a4ca80186f\",\"c86f56c6-5257-485f-8eb8-6287cf6e19b2\",\"f0d94db3-c9d8-4635-8314-24a733f75474\",\"95f63445-23bd-463e-a47b-ae69175d211b\",\"5ad23dc5-9502-4c46-9463-4bf96c7f4005\",\"068f6f17-cb0c-42ab-9e12-f9e616668ad6\",\"a5d2bb4a-3c9a-41d5-bcb5-3cf6d5b44f83\",\"b8d81d1a-6e91-4b18-b6e7-f275f87f05a2\",\"553eac2d-c469-4ca4-852a-f7544f0a797b\",\"36a08bec-8623-48f8-bc0f-a303cbdf53bc\",\"ff25bad9-2b22-4a6a-a198-cb2631c59c8e\",\"849b3aa4-f54f-4447-b60b-5d96a7feec89\",\"73c81f93-f118-4ad3-9b59-c8c54393a8c7\",\"9043ddd9-1986-445b-9ce0-946ce69774de\",\"69d341c8-6f43-4469-b888-f2fef43787c3\",\"59ec712b-7339-4983-9d48-63853c0a57cd\",\"05ac3dfc-25c3-4dd6-acfb-31f4f2fa2a6f\"]',\n    'Consumer IDs approved for Allianz insurance benefit testing (29 users: 11 subscribed + 18 non-subscribed)',\n    0\n)\nON CONFLICT (key) DO UPDATE SET\n    value = EXCLUDED.value,\n    description = EXCLUDED.description,\n    update_date = now(),\n    version = configuration.version + 1;\n\nINSERT INTO configuration (key, value, description)\nVALUES\n    -- Enable notification job (processes insurance benefit notifications)\n    ('BENEFIT_INSURANCE_ALLIANZ_NOTIFICATION_JOB_ENABLED', 'true',\n     'Enable Allianz insurance notification processing job'),\n\nON CONFLICT (key) DO UPDATE\n    SET value = EXCLUDED.value,\n        description = EXCLUDED.description,\n        update_date = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP;\n\n\n\n-- ============================================================================\n-- 2. PARTNER EXPORT JOBS (for CSV exports to SFTP)\n-- ============================================================================\n\nINSERT INTO configuration (key, value, description)\nVALUES\n    -- Enable stale lock cleanup (cleans up stuck export records)\n    ('PARTNER_EXPORT_STALE_LOCK_CLEANUP_JOB_ENABLED', 'true',\n     'Enable cleanup job for stale export locks'),\n\n    -- Enable record creation job (creates export records for each plan level)\n    ('PARTNER_EXPORT_ALLIANZ_CREATE_RECORDS_JOB_ENABLED', 'true',\n     'Enable job to create Allianz export records'),\n\n    -- Enable export job (exports data to S3)\n    ('PARTNER_EXPORT_ALLIANZ_EXPORT_JOB_ENABLED', 'true',\n     'Enable job to export Allianz data to S3'),\n\n    -- Enable upload job (uploads from S3 to SFTP)\n    ('PARTNER_EXPORT_ALLIANZ_UPLOAD_JOB_ENABLED', 'true',\n     'Enable job to upload Allianz exports to SFTP')\nON CONFLICT (key) DO UPDATE\n    SET value = EXCLUDED.value,\n        description = EXCLUDED.description,\n        update_date = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP;\n```\n\n","project":{"id":213168,"name":"[satispay_plus][prod] - Insurance Allianz - Bootstrap - Phase 1"},"entityState":{"id":213168,"name":"[satispay_plus][prod] - Insurance Allianz - Bootstrap - Phase 1"}},{"id":213050,"name":"[satispay_plus][prod] Configure aws_s3 extensions","description":"<!--markdown--># WHY \n\nIn order to use `aws_s3` inside RDS.\n\n# WHAT\n\n```sql\nCREATE EXTENSION IF NOT EXISTS aws_s3 CASCADE;\nGRANT USAGE ON SCHEMA aws_s3 TO service_rw;\nGRANT EXECUTE ON FUNCTION aws_s3.query_export_to_s3(text, text, text, text, text, text, out bigint, out bigint, out bigint) TO service_rw;\n```","project":{"id":213050,"name":"[satispay_plus][prod] Configure aws_s3 extensions"},"entityState":{"id":213050,"name":"[satispay_plus][prod] Configure aws_s3 extensions"}}]}
